quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,48,yeh pehlay bhi taalib fasaad rahay hain aur bohat si baton mein tumahray liye ulat phair karte rahay hain. yahan taq ke haq aap_hncha aur khuda ka hukum ghalib howa aur woh bura mantay hi reh gay
  9,49,aur un mein koi aisa bhi hai jo kehta hai ke mujhe to ijazat hi dijiye aur aafat mein nah dalye. dekho yeh aafat mein prhgye hain aur dozakh sab kafiroon ko ghairay hue hai
  9,50,( ae paighambar ) agar tum ko asayish haasil hoti hai to un ko buri lagti hai. aur koi mushkil padtee hai to kehte ke hum ne apna kaam pehlay hain ( durust ) kar liya tha aur khusihyan manate lout jatay hain
  9,51,keh do ke hum ko koi museebat nahi poanch sakti bajuz is ke jo khuda ne hamaray liye likh di ho wohi hamara karsaaz hai. aur mominon ko khuda hi ka bharosa rakhna chahiye
  9,52,keh do ke tum hamaray haq mein do bhulaiyon mein se aik ke munhtazir ho aur hum tumahray haq mein is baat ke munhtazir hain ke khuda ( ya to ) apne paas se tum par koi azaab nazil kere ya hamaray hathon se ( azaab dlwaye ) to tum bhi intzaar karo hum bhi tumahray sath intzaar karte hain
  9,53,keh do ke tum ( maal ) khusi se kharch karo ya na khushi se tum se hargiz qubool nahikiya jaye ga tum nafarman log ho
  9,54,aur un ke kharch ( mwal ) ke qubool honay se koi cheez Maney nahi hui siwa is ke unhon ne khuda se aur is ke rasool se kufarkiya aur namaz ko atay hain to sust kaahil hokar aur kharch karte hain to na khushi se
